          "reviewBody": "Euro school cbse wakad is one of the best school in this area. My experience with Euro so far is best, School staff always makes sure to respond on time and keep parents up-to-date with all the upcoming planned activities. My kid enjoys going school and loves doing all the activities and curriculum being taught. Teachers in the school are very supportive and well trained, they treat students well and make sure that children learns all the concepts clearly.  Thanks to all the teachers, staff and principal mam for keeping things up to mark.",
