            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We took admission for my son in grade 3 and lockdown started, we were so worried about the studies and other activities but the school was ready with their online platform within less than a month and kids enjoyed their online school too. Euroschool brings out the best in every child by tapping into their individual strengths, while creating an environment of kindness, responsibility, and leadership. We are so happy with school, all teachers and supportive staff. We have seen lot of improvement in our son after joining Euroschool.",
          "publisher": {
