            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school is very good in terms of activities. Academic is encouraged along with activities so that kids doesn’t get bored. But there has to be good break between academic and activities for kids to participate every time with fresh energy. My kids like the school they don’t want to shift anywhere else . Thank you EURO proud of you and continue growing new standards 👍🏻👍🏻🇮🇳🇮🇳😊happy Independence Day",
          "publisher": {
