          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-16",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Our experience at Euro School has been exceptional. The teachers are truly invested in all students education and their growth as learners.\nAdjustments are made as needed to meet the needs of the student\nSmall class sizes and leveled learning have enabley children to gain confidence in their learning abilities.\nThe administration is open minded and think outside the box to make Euro school a successful educational experience for the students Euro school is committed to the whole child. They teach value lessons, communication and leadership skills.\nThanks to all",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "EuroSchool Bhumkar Chowk - Marunji Village,Hinjawadi"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Amardeep Tiwari"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Fantastic school!! The teachers are very professional, caring, well organized. Having nice infrastructure & wonderful atmosphere for the kids.\nThe admissions process was outstanding, they really care and genuinely want the best for the kids.\nMy both kids are with the school in 1st and 2nd Standard. I am very satisfied by seeing improvement and remarkable confidence level & overall personality development, speaking skills and physical activity.\nEvery day my kids are looking forward to coming to the school. They very much enjoy their time in school and learning new things every day. They participate in a variety of activities and events and enjoy both their teachers and classmates company. They are having a great time and lots of fun too!\nA wide range of extra curriculars activities to enhance the kids passions to the next level. There are lot of social events like Yoga, Dances, Sports and lot more events under experienced instructors.\nI appreciate all the teachers and management for the efforts they are putting in and I would like to extend my gratitude towards School and wish and hope that these extended efforts would continue!!\nI strongly recommend Euro School CBSE Wakad who want a wonderful start for their kids.",
